<h2>Beloved/Encounters</h2>
<div id="line2"></div>
<div id="box2">
<a href="#blanket7" style="background-image:url(https://i.imgur.com/WF5YV9w.png); border:1px solid #fff; border-radius:10px;"></a>

<a href="#blanket8" style="background-image:url(https://i.imgur.com/OgJdkZy.png); border:1px solid #fff; border-radius:10px;"></a>

